## Step 7: Create playbook

```bash id="7q1e2y"
nano deploy.yml
```

Paste:

```yaml id="3c8w0k"
- name: Deploy Maven Artifact
  hosts: web

  tasks:
    - name: Create deployment directory
      file:
        path: /var/jenkins_home/deploy
        state: directory
        mode: '0755'

    - name: Copy artifact
      copy:
        src: target/jenkins-ansible-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar
        dest: /var/jenkins_home/deploy/jenkins-ansible.jar
```

Save.

(as shown page 2) 

