# PART 6: Create Jenkins Pipeline

---

## Step 15: Create job

* Click **New Item**
* Enter name
* Select **Pipeline**
* Click OK

---

## Step 16: Add Pipeline Script

Paste:

```groovy id="9v2m5k"
pipeline {
    agent any

    tools {
        maven 'Maven-3.9'
    }

    stages {

        stage('Checkout Code') {
            steps {
                git 'https://github.com/username/repo.git'
            }
        }

        stage('Build Maven Project') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn clean package'
            }
        }

        stage('Deploy using Ansible') {
            steps {
                sh 'ansible-playbook deploy.yml -i inventory'
            }
        }
    }
}
```

Replace:

```
username/repo
```

(as shown page 3–4) 

Click **Save**

